---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-content">
		<div class="footer-brand">
			<span class="brand-icon">🛡️</span>
			<span>KalaSpace Sec</span>
			<p class="footer-desc">网络安全知识库 · 漏洞情报中心</p>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-links">
			<div class="footer-col">
				<h4>漏洞库</h4>
				<a href="/vul">漏洞总览</a>
				<a href="/vul/cms">CMS漏洞</a>
				<a href="/vul/editor">编辑器漏洞</a>
				<a href="/vul/middleware">中间件/框架</a>
				<a href="/vul/product">产品/工具</a>
				<a href="/vul/system">系统漏洞</a>
				<a href="/vul/iot">IoT/设备</a>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-col">
				<h4>知识库</h4>
				<a href="/kb">知识总览</a>
				<a href="/kb/web-security">Web安全</a>
				<a href="/kb/penetration">渗透测试</a>
				<a href="/kb/reverse">逆向工程</a>
				<a href="/kb/ctf">CTF笔记</a>
				<a href="/kb/cheatsheet">速查表</a>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-col">
				<h4>资源</h4>
				<a href="/kb/ports">端口速查</a>
				<a href="/kb/shells">WebShell查杀</a>
				<a href="/kb/waf-bypass">WAF绕过</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/qwerasdzx-123/kalaspace-blog" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="footer-bottom">
		<p>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} KalaSpace Sec · 仅供安全研究与学习使用</p>
		<p class="footer-note">⚠️ 请遵守当地法律法规，未经授权禁止用于非法渗透测试</p>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		padding: 3em 1.5em 2em;
		background: var(--bg-card);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
		margin-top: 4em;
	}
	.footer-content {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
		gap: 3em;
		padding-bottom: 2em;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
	}
	.footer-brand .brand-icon {
		font-size: 1.5em;
	}
	.footer-brand span {
		font-size: 1.2em;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.footer-desc {
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.85em;
		margin-top: 0.5em;
	}
	.footer-links {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2em;
	}
	.footer-col h4 {
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: 0.85em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		margin-bottom: 0.8em;
	}
	.footer-col a {
		display: block;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.88em;
		padding: 0.25em 0;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}
	.footer-col a:hover {
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.footer-bottom {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 1.5em auto 0;
		text-align: center;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.82em;
	}
	.footer-note {
		color: rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.7);
		margin-top: 0.3em;
	}
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.footer-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2em; }
		.footer-links { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
	}
	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.footer-links { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
	}
</style>
